# ======================
# Instructions
# ======================
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace all "changeme_*" values with secure random strings
# 3. Generate OAuth secrets with: openssl rand -hex 32
# 4. Hash OAuth secrets for Authelia with:
#    docker run --rm authelia/authelia:latest authelia crypto hash generate pbkdf2 --variant sha512 --password 'YOUR_SECRET'
# 5. Update configs/authelia/configuration.yml with hashed secrets
# 6. Generate RSA key pair:
#    openssl genrsa -out private.pem 4096
#    openssl rsa -in private.pem -pubout -out public.pem
# 7. Add the private key content to AUTHELIA_OIDC_ISSUER_PRIVATE_KEY
